job.title: West Central Railway Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 716 Trade Apprentice Posts
job.body:
Total Vacancies:716

Name of the post:

  • Various apprentice vacancies

Description:

The West Central Railway issued a total of 716 vacancies for the posts of the apprentice. The online application for these posts under West Central Railway has started. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 30-04-2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The interested candidates after filling the application form, it is required to pay the application fee to complete the form submission process:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • The application fee for the SC/ST/PWD/ Female candidates is INR 70/-
  • The application fee for others is INR 170
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 27-03-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 30-04-2021

Educational qualification required:

Candidates who are interested to apply should have the following qualification from a recognized University/boards with valid marks :

  • You must have a diploma in 10th Class with ITI (Relevant Trade) to apply for the post of the apprentice

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is 15 Years
  • The maximum age required to apply is 24 years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per the 7th pay commission for the post of the apprentice is as per norms
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that West Central Railway issued this notification for which posts.

 

How to apply for West Central Railway Trade Apprentice Online Form 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of West Central Railway.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of the apprentice.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
